# 1. Pre-Calculus

## Functions & Transformations

| Concept | Formula |
|------|--------|
| Function | \( f: A \to B \) |
| Composition | \( (f\circ g)(x)=f(g(x)) \) |
| Inverse | \( f^{-1}(f(x))=x \) |
| Even | \( f(-x)=f(x) \) |
| Odd | \( f(-x)=-f(x) \) |
| Vertical shift | \( f(x)+c \) |
| Horizontal shift | \( f(x-c) \) |
| Vertical scale | \( af(x) \) |
| Horizontal scale | \( f(ax) \) |

---

## Exponents & Radicals

| Rule | Formula |
|----|--------|
| Product | \( a^m a^n=a^{m+n} \) |
| Quotient | \( \frac{a^m}{a^n}=a^{m-n} \) |
| Power of power | \( (a^m)^n=a^{mn} \) |
| Negative exponent | \( a^{-n}=\frac1{a^n} \) |
| Zero exponent | \( a^0=1 \) |
| Rational exponent | \( a^{m/n}=\sqrt[n]{a^m} \) |
| Square root | \( \sqrt{a^2}=|a| \) |

---

## Logarithms

| Rule | Formula |
|----|--------|
| Definition | \( \log_a x=y \iff a^y=x \) |
| Product | \( \log(ab)=\log a+\log b \) |
| Quotient | \( \log(a/b)=\log a-\log b \) |
| Power | \( \log(a^k)=k\log a \) |
| Change of base | \( \log_a b=\frac{\log b}{\log a} \) |
| Inverse | \( \log(a^x)=x,\ a^{\log x}=x \) |

---

## Trigonometry

| Identity | Formula |
|--------|--------|
| Unit circle | \( (\cos\theta,\sin\theta) \) |
| Pythagorean | \( \sin^2\theta+\cos^2\theta=1 \) |
| Tangent | \( \tan\theta=\frac{\sin\theta}{\cos\theta} \) |
| Angle sum (sin) | \( \sin(\alpha+\beta)=\sin\alpha\cos\beta+\cos\alpha\sin\beta \) |
| Angle sum (cos) | \( \cos(\alpha+\beta)=\cos\alpha\cos\beta-\sin\alpha\sin\beta \) |
| Double angle | \( \sin2\theta=2\sin\theta\cos\theta \) |
| Euler | \( e^{i\theta}=\cos\theta+i\sin\theta \) |

