# 4. Series & Convergence

## Definitions

| Concept | Formula |
|------|--------|
| Partial sum | \( S_n=\sum_{k=1}^n a_k \) |
| Convergence | \( \lim_{n\to\infty} S_n=S \) |
| Necessary condition | \( a_k\to0 \) |

---

## Standard Series

| Series | Result |
|------|--------|
| Geometric | converges iff \( |r|<1 \) |
| Harmonic | diverges |
| p-series | converges iff \( p>1 \) |

---

## Comparison Tests

| Test | Criterion |
|----|-----------|
| Direct | \( 0\le a_k\le b_k \), \( \sum b_k \) conv ⇒ \( \sum a_k \) conv |
| Limit | \( \lim \frac{a_k}{b_k}=c>0 \Rightarrow \) same behavior |

---

## Ratio & Root Tests

| Test | Criterion |
|----|-----------|
| Ratio | \( L=\lim\left|\frac{a_{k+1}}{a_k}\right| \) |
| Root | \( L=\limsup\sqrt[k]{|a_k|} \) |
| Result | \( L<1 \) conv, \( L>1 \) div |

---

## Integral Test

| Condition | Result |
|----|--------|
| \( f(k)=a_k \), positive, decreasing | \( \sum a_k \) conv ⇔ \( \int f \) conv |

---

## Alternating Series

| Concept | Condition |
|------|-----------|
| Alternating test | decreasing \( a_k \), \( a_k\to0 \) |
| Absolute convergence | \( \sum|a_k| \) conv |
| Conditional convergence | \( \sum a_k \) conv, \( \sum|a_k| \) div |

---

## Power & Taylor Series

| Concept | Formula |
|------|--------|
| Power series | \( \sum a_k(x-c)^k \) |
| Radius | \( R=\lim\left|\frac{a_k}{a_{k+1}}\right| \) |
| Taylor | \( \sum \frac{f^{(k)}(a)}{k!}(x-a)^k \) |
| Maclaurin | \( a=0 \) |

